{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An ancient evil has awakened, causing a blight to spread across the land. You are one of the wizards from the Arcanum with the only weapon that can stop it. Defend against hordes of monsters in a desperate last stand. Summon towers, build walls, cast spells, and change the terrain to defeat your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688710/extras/enemy_spawning3.gif?t=1737578092\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Change the Terrain</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the terrain to your advantage and change it however you want. Raise, lower, or level the ground to build your defenses and take the high ground. Change the enemies path and funnel them into killzones. But beware, some monsters can change the terrain too and will try to break through your walls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688710/extras/terraforming2.gif?t=1737578092\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Elemental Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find elemental runes to increase the power of your spells. Runes come in different rarities and imbue your towers with elemental status effects. Burn, Slow, Poison and Mark your foes or increase the stats of your towers. Mix and match different elemental runes to create powerful combinations and improve your defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688710/extras/elemental_attacks1.gif?t=1737578092\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Randomly Generated Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each mission is randomly generated with different terrain, resources, and enemies. Adjust to the ever shifting terrain, and take the high ground!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2